{\"begin\": 3417, \"end\": 3451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_National_Olympic_Council\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Singapore National Olympic Council\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_National_Olympic_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_National_Olympic_Council\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fom\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3303}, {\"ngram\": \"their assessment\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3492}, {\"ngram\": \"a wrap-up press conference\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3526}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ST PHOTO: MARK CHEONG While Mr Tan called for perspective - \\\"to be here competing against the best is hard, to win is damn bloody hard\\\" - Mr Chan urged top Singapore athletes to capitalise on the one-off nature of the Olympics, as opposed to season-long tours and competitions, and take the opportunity to pull off surprises.\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3681, \"end\": 3685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Chan\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 1.4419457375539427e-12, \"text\": \"Chan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Chan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Chan\"}, {\"begin\": 3696, \"end\": 3705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4339628042643705e-29, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ST PHOTO\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3547}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr Tan\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3573}, {\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3596}, {\"ngram\": \"the one-off nature\", \"from\": 3731, \"to\": 3749}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3765}, {\"ngram\": \"season-long tours\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3798}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 3815}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 3826, \"to\": 3841}, {\"ngram\": \"surprises\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 3863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were 15 Olympic debutants in the contingent, with four still teenagers.\", \"from\": 3867, \"to\": 3944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"15 Olympic debutants\", \"from\": 3878, \"to\": 3898}, {\"ngram\": \"the contingent\", \"from\": 3902, \"to\": 3916}, {\"ngram\": \"four still teenagers\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 3943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr Su noted: \\\"Yes, we need to string together the consistency and winning touch... We may not have fully done so in each of our athletes' performances.\", \"from\": 3945, \"to\": 4096, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dr Su\", \"from\": 3945, \"to\": 3950}, {\"ngram\": \"the consistency\", \"from\": 3991, \"to\": 4006}, {\"ngram\": \"touch\", \"from\": 4019, \"to\": 4024}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes' performances\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you track each of their performance profiles in the last one to two years, you will see that at the regional and even Asian levels, we have overcome higher-ranked opponents.\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4220, \"end\": 4225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2334530313503872e-20, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their performance profiles\", \"from\": 4120, \"to\": 4146}, {\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 4166, \"to\": 4175}, {\"ngram\": \"higher-ranked opponents\", \"from\": 4251, \"to\": 4274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And this is exactly what we need to build on at their first Olympics, to go away with knowing how to win at the critical moment and be ruthless about it.\", \"from\": 4276, \"to\": 4429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 4288, \"to\": 4300}, {\"ngram\": \"their first Olympics\", \"from\": 4324, \"to\": 4344}, {\"ngram\": \"the critical moment\", \"from\": 4384, \"to\": 4403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They have an indomitable fighting spirit.\", \"from\": 4431, \"to\": 4473, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an indomitable fighting spirit\", \"from\": 4442, \"to\": 4472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I agree that learning to win, the winning part takes experience, and our consolation and optimism is that our cohort of athletes here is very young.\", \"from\": 4474, \"to\": 4626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the winning part\", \"from\": 4508, \"to\": 4524}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 4531, \"to\": 4541}, {\"ngram\": \"our consolation\", \"from\": 4547, \"to\": 4562}, {\"ngram\": \"optimism\", \"from\": 4567, \"to\": 4575}, {\"ngram\": \"our cohort\", \"from\": 4584, \"to\": 4594}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 4598, \"to\": 4606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What is important is that the new wind for Singapore sports must catalyse cohort over cohort of new blood who are fearless and are able to dream big.\\\"\", \"from\": 4628, \"to\": 4779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4672, \"end\": 4681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4339628042643705e-29, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the new wind\", \"from\": 4655, \"to\": 4667}, {\"ngram\": \"cohort\", \"from\": 4715, \"to\": 4721}, {\"ngram\": \"new blood\", \"from\": 4725, \"to\": 4734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Badminton player Loh Kean Yew also performed admirably to reach the knockout rounds.\", \"from\": 4781, \"to\": 4865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4798, \"end\": 4810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loh_Kean_Yew\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Loh Kean Yew\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loh_Kean_Yew\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loh_Kean_Yew\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the knockout rounds\", \"from\": 4845, \"to\": 4864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: ST FILE Reviews will be conducted ahead of the 2025 SEA Games and 2026 Asian Games and Mr Tan suggested that Singapore, which does not have the talent depth of bigger countries, look at future Olympic programmes and seize the opportunity to be \\\"ahead of the curve\\\" with niche sports like kitefoiling and skateboarding.\", \"from\": 4867, \"to\": 5193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4984, \"end\": 4993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4339628042643705e-29, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 4867, \"to\": 4872}, {\"ngram\": \"ST FILE Reviews\", \"from\": 4874, \"to\": 4889}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2025 SEA Games\", \"from\": 4917, \"to\": 4935}, {\"ngram\": \"2026 Asian Games\", \"from\": 4940, \"to\": 4956}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr Tan\", \"from\": 4961, \"to\": 4967}, {\"ngram\": \"the talent depth\", \"from\": 5014, \"to\": 5030}, {\"ngram\": \"bigger countries\", \"from\": 5034, \"to\": 5050}, {\"ngram\": \"future Olympic programmes\", \"from\": 5060, \"to\": 5085}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 5096, \"to\": 5111}, {\"ngram\": \"the curve\", \"from\": 5128, \"to\": 5137}, {\"ngram\": \"niche sports\", \"from\": 5144, \"to\": 5156}, {\"ngram\": \"kitefoiling\", \"from\": 5162, \"to\": 5173}, {\"ngram\": \"skateboarding\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women medallists in skateboarding were all aged 14 to 16.\", \"from\": 5194, \"to\": 5255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The women\", \"from\": 5194, \"to\": 5203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"We could not do everything, we tried to do some things.\", \"from\": 5257, \"to\": 5322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 5283, \"to\": 5293}, {\"ngram\": \"some things\", \"from\": 5310, \"to\": 5321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's an important step.\", \"from\": 5323, \"to\": 5348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an important step\", \"from\": 5330, \"to\": 5347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a system, we learn.\", \"from\": 5349, \"to\": 5371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a system\", \"from\": 5352, \"to\": 5360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's how fast we learn as well.\", \"from\": 5372, \"to\": 5403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is high performance sports - every waking moment, there is somebody out there waiting to steal your lunch.\", \"from\": 5404, \"to\": 5515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high performance sports\", \"from\": 5412, \"to\": 5435}, {\"ngram\": \"every waking moment\", \"from\": 5438, \"to\": 5457}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 5468, \"to\": 5476}, {\"ngram\": \"your lunch\", \"from\": 5504, \"to\": 5514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Singapore, we are starting to see more and more kids and parents willing to take that journey.\", \"from\": 5517, \"to\": 5615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5521, \"end\": 5530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4339628042643705e-29, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more and more kids\", \"from\": 5555, \"to\": 5573}, {\"ngram\": \"parents\", \"from\": 5578, \"to\": 5585}, {\"ngram\": \"that journey\", \"from\": 5602, \"to\": 5614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That'